<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>개인 정보 수정 페이지</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>개인 정보 수정 하기</h1>
<p>사용자 ID: {{user.User_Id}}</p>
<p>사용자 이름: {{user.User_Name}}</p>
<form method="post" action="/update-profile">

    <label for="userEmail">Email:</label>
    <input type="email" id="userEmail" name="User_Email" value="{{user.User_Email}}" required>

    <br>
    <br>
    <label for="userAddress">Address:</label>
    <input type="text" id="userAddress" name="User_Address" value="{{user.User_Address}}" required>

    <br>
    <br>
    <label for="userPhone">Phone:</label>
    <input type="text" id="userPhone" name="User_Phone" value="{{user.User_Phone}}" required>

    <br>
    <p>보유 마일리지: {{user.User_Mileage}}</p>

    <input type="submit" value="Update Profile">
</form>
</body>
</html>
